• Prioritize high-value, in-market accounts
• Reduce wasted spend on low-intent leads
• Personalize outreach with contextual relevance

Instead of reacting late, intent-based marketing helps teams proactively engage when interest is peaking.

Intent-based marketing aligns sales and marketing

