• Launch account-based marketing (ABM) campaigns
• Deliver content aligned to current research topics

Sales teams benefit by:

• Receiving warmer, context-rich leads
• Timing outreach based on active interest
• Increasing connect and conversion rates

This alignment is a core pillar of successful ABM and full-funnel demand generation programs.

